Suite/Test/Step Name: Test Cases/Main Test Cases/TC1_Verify Successful Login_With TestOps Vision
Description:
Verify if users can login successful. 

Steps:
- Click on 'Book Appointment' button to login
- Input username and password
- Click on 'Login' button

Expected result:
'Appointment' section is displayed after successful login

Suite/Test/Step Name: comment("Given that the user has the valid login information")
comment("When he logins to CURA system")
comment("Then he should be able to login successfully")
Test Cases/Main Test Cases/TC2_Verify Successful Appointment_With TestOps Vision
Description:
Verify if users can book an appointment sucessfully.
Pre-condition: Users have already logged in

Steps:
- Fill in appoinment's information
- Click on appointment's button

Expected results:
Appointment Confirmation page is displayed

Suite/Test/Step Name: comment("Given that the user has logged into their account")
setText(findTestObject("Page_CuraAppointment/txt_Comment"), "Please make appointment as soon as possible.")
comment("When he fills in valid information in Appointment page")
comment("Then he should be able to book a new appointment")
verifyMatch("Please make appointment as soon as possible.", getText(findTestObject("Page_AppointmentConfirmation/lbl_Comment")), false)
